createNamespaceDescription_iks: Add a single namespace or multiple namespaces to your specific namespace's list.
createNamespaceDescription_roks: Add a single project or multiple projects to your specific project's list.
enterNamespace_iks: Enter namespaces separated by a comma. After you click Add, the new namespaces are included in the list and automatically selected.
enterNamespace_roks: Enter projects separated by a comma. After you click Add, the new projects are included in the list and automatically selected.
invalidNamespace_iks: The name of a namespace can include only lowercase letters, numbers, and dashes. The name can't start or end with a dash, and it must be at a maximum of 63 characters.
invalidNamespace_roks: The name of a project can include only lowercase letters, numbers, and dashes. The name can't start or end with a dash, and it must be at a maximum of 63 characters.
fetchErrorDescription_iks: The list of namespaces can't be populated. Try again later.
fetchErrorDescription_roks: The list of projects can't be populated. Try again later.
